body_html: I think you should be able to see the status Import/copybara as it transitions from one state to the other. It's a manual, multi-step process of reviewing the changes for security, running tests, and getting approvals. It's maybe one hour in the fastest case. In this instance, I forgot to check back and approve the first level. After that, it will need to pass tests and get another approval.
